Lab: Configure Network Security

1. Architecture of the Lab
Two microservices exist:
External User
      │
      ▼
OpenShift Router
      │
      ▼
product service (product pod)
      │
 HTTPS
      ▼
stock service (stock pod)
Microservices
Service	Purpose
product	API entry point
stock	returns stock information
Example response:
{
"id":1,
"name":"rpi4_4gb",
"stock":10
}
If product cannot contact stock:
stock = -1
________________________________________
2. Lab Objectives
You must configure:
Security Feature	Purpose
TLS service certificate	encrypt internal traffic
OpenShift CA injection	trust TLS certificates
External TLS route	expose API securely
Network Policies	restrict pod communication
________________________________________
