23. Configure Network Policy for Stock
We allow only product pods to access stock.
Edit:
stock-ingresspolicy.yaml
apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: NetworkPolicy
metadata:
  name: ingress-stock-policy
spec:
  podSelector:
    matchLabels:
      app: stock
  ingress:
  - from:
    - podSelector:
        matchLabels:
          app: product
    ports:
    - protocol: TCP
      port: 8085
________________________________________
Apply:
oc create -f stock-ingresspolicy.yaml
________________________________________
24. Configure Network Policy for Product
Only router pods can access product.
Edit:
product-ingresspolicy.yaml
apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: NetworkPolicy
metadata:
  name: product-ingress-policy
spec:
  podSelector:
    matchLabels:
      app: product
  ingress:
  - from:
    - namespaceSelector:
        matchLabels:
          policy-group.network.openshift.io/ingress: ""
    ports:
    - protocol: TCP
      port: 8080
________________________________________
Apply:
oc create -f product-ingresspolicy.yaml
________________________________________
25. Final Secure Architecture
External User
     │
     ▼
Router (TLS passthrough)
     │
     ▼
Product Pod (HTTPS)
     │
     ▼
Stock Pod (HTTPS)

Network Policies:
Router -> Product only
Product -> Stock only
